Senator Dino Melaye, the lawmaker representing Kogi West Senatorial District in Kogi State has surrendered to the Police, Daily Trust gathered. The senator is presently in the custody of the Nigeria Police Force. A source at the Force Headquarters in Abuja who confirmed this to the press on Friday, also hinted that Melaye has been taken to the office of the Federal Special Anti-Robbery Squad (FSARS) in Guzape. Details soon… Dino is being arrested over attempted murder – Police Police to declare Dino wanted Police to declare Dino wanted